colophon_(төгсгөлийн_үг): @174A *, ,(SNYAN NGAG ME LONG GI DKA' 'GREL DBYANGS CAN DGYES PA'I GLU DBYANGS 'DI NYID, LAM 'DI'I PHYOGS TZAM MI SHES RUNG DANG ZHEN SHIN TU CHE BA BSTAN PA RGYAL MTSAN ZHES BYA BAS, RTZA BA NANG DU YOD TSE BLTA BDE BAS BLO GSAL YONGS LA PHAN DU RE ZHING, ^THAMS CAD MKHYEN PA'I DGONGS PA DANG YANG MI 'GAL SNYAM NAS GTZOS DGA' LDAN CHOS GLING DU GANG CI'I KHUR LEN BYAS TE RAB YID CHU KHYI LOR PAR GSAR DU BSKRUN PA'I DGE BAS RGYAL BSTAN RIN PO CHE 'DI NYID PHYOGS DUS GNAS SKABS KUN DU DAR ZHING RGYAS LA YUN RING DU GNAS PA DANG, LUS CAN MTHA' DAG MA RIG RMONGS MUN SANGS TE RNAM PA THAMS CAD MKHYEN PA'I GO 'PHANG THOB PA'I RGYUR GYUR CIG DZA YANTU,, ,,)
